---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MEDSEN Foundation" lang="en" description="The MEDSEN Foundation carries our commitment to children's rights, anchored in the Convention on the Rights of the Child.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 via-amber-400 to-senegal-yellow text-gray-900 py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <pattern id="dots" width="4" height="4" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <circle cx="2" cy="2" r="0.5" fill="currentColor"/>
        </pattern>
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#dots)"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.293z"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold">MEDSEN Foundation</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6">
          Our commitment<br/>to children's rights.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 max-w-2xl">
          Building software is not enough. The MEDSEN Foundation carries our commitment
          beyond the platform itself, anchored in the
          <strong>Convention on the Rights of the Child</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why a Foundation -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">Our intention</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Why a Foundation?
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-5">
        <p>
          We want our activity to contribute, in our measure, to concrete actions for children.
          That is the purpose of the MEDSEN Foundation: to carry that commitment in a distinct,
          legible way, aligned with the principles of the
          <strong>Convention on the Rights of the Child</strong>, ratified by Senegal in 1990.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-base italic">
          The Foundation is being structured. Its precise modalities (legal form, governance,
          forms of engagement) will be defined and published when it becomes operational.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Framework: CRC -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block bg-sante-100 text-sante-700 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">Our framework</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          The Convention on the Rights of the Child.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Adopted by the United Nations in 1989 and ratified by Senegal in 1990, the CRC sets
          out the fundamental rights every child should enjoy. We refer to it explicitly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-amber-100">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-600 mb-2">Article 3</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Best interests of the child</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Every decision concerning a child must be made in their best interests.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-amber-100">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-600 mb-2">Article 24</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Right to health</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Every child has the right to the highest attainable standard of health and access to care.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-amber-100">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-600 mb-2">Article 28</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Right to education</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Health conditions schooling. Protecting a child's health protects their right to learn.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our commitment (humble) -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <span class="inline-block bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">Our commitment</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          A share of our activity dedicated to the Foundation.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          We commit to dedicating a regular share of our results to funding the MEDSEN
          Foundation. The exact percentage, schedule and areas of intervention will be
          formalized and made public once the Foundation is operational.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-amber-500">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center text-gray-900">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Let's discuss the Foundation
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8">
        You work on children's rights and want to talk? Get in touch.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-lg transition-colors">
        Contact us
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
